al properties derived\nfrom optical data, the Ophiuchus cluster seems to be overall a relaxed\nstructure, or at most a minor merger, though in X-rays the central region\n(radius ~ 150 kpc) may show evidence for merging effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2015 08:46:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
